{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:0","text":"与所有 texture style nodes（纹理样式节点）一样，此节点接收一个 manifold，用来描述应用 Worley noise 纹理的 2D 或 3D 域。如果未连接 manifold，默认行为是在 3D 中沿 P 应用。此节点会计算"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:1","text":"Worley noise"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:2","text":"，如 Steven Worley 所描述。"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:3","text":"Input Parameters"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:4","text":"Surface Position"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:5","text":"noise 可基于"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:6","text":"Current Position"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:7","text":"或"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:8","text":"Undisplaced Position"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:9","text":"（表面置换之前的位置）来计算。"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:10","text":"如果你希望 displacement 和 shading patterns 匹配，请使用"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:11","text":"Undisplaced Position"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:12","text":"。"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:13","text":"Frequency"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:14","text":"控制 cells 的尺寸。频率越高，cells 越小。"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:15","text":"Distance Metric"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:16","text":"用于测量到相邻 cells 距离的方式。Manhattan distance 会产生更矩形的形状，而 Euclidean distance 会产生更球形的形状。"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:17","text":"Euclidean"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:18","text":"计算到最近点的 Euclidean distance。它看起来比 Squared Euclidean distance 更尖一些。"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:19","text":"Euclidean Squared"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:20","text":"计算到最近点的 squared Euclidean distance。它看起来比纯 Euclidean distance 更圆润，也更有机。"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:21","text":"Manhattan"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:22","text":"受 Manhattan 网格式组织启发，这是当你只能沿 cell 边界移动时，到最近点的距离。"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:23","text":"Chebyshev"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:24","text":"命名自"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:25","text":"Pafnutty Chebyshev"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:26","text":"，也称为 Chessboard Distance（棋盘距离）。它有点类似 Manhattan distance，但旋转了 45 度。"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:27","text":"Minkowski"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:28","text":"Minkowski"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:29","text":"是 Euclidean 和 Manhattan distance 的一种泛化。该 exponent 会使图案从 Euclidean 过渡到 Manhattan。"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:30","text":"Minkowski 比其他 distance metrics 更昂贵，但用于 displacement 时是可以接受的，因为几何体被置换时你只会支付一次成本。"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:31","text":"Jitter"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:32","text":"控制 cells 的扭曲。"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:33","text":"C1"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:34","text":"到第一个 feature（特征点）距离的乘数。"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:35","text":"C2"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:36","text":"到第二个 feature（特征点）距离的乘数。"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:37","text":"Minkowski Exponent"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:38","text":"使 distance 从 Manhattan (1.0) 平滑过渡到 Euclidean (2.0)，再到一些奇特的未探索区域。"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:39","text":"Shape"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:40","text":"修改计算出的 distances 以创建不同形状。下面示例使用 c1 = 1.0 和 c2 = 0.0。"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:41","text":"Clamp Output"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:42","text":"使生成的 distances 被 clamp 到 0.0 到 1.0 范围内。"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:43","text":"c1"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:44","text":"c2"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:45","text":"distancemetric"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:46","text":": Euclidean"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:47","text":"Invert"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:48","text":"反转最终 pattern。"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:49","text":"Random Scale"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:50","text":"这会随机缩放 features（特征点）的振幅，并产生稍微更规则的外观。"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:51","text":"Random Scale Center"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:52","text":"这会在应用 random scale 之前对 signal 应用一个 offset。用它可以创建更多变化。"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:53","text":"Manifold"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:54","text":"用于应用 noise 的 manifold。（默认值为 P）。"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:55","text":"可以连接 3D 或 2D manifold。"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:56","text":"Adjust Output"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:57","text":"Color Scale"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:58","text":"纹理颜色值的乘数，可用于调整亮度或操控单独的颜色通道"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:59","text":"Color Offset"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:60","text":"对结果应用 offset，使结果的颜色发生偏移"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:61","text":"Float Scale"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:62","text":"标量 Float 值"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:63","text":"Float Offset"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:64","text":"Float Offset 值"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:65","text":"Output Parameters"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:66","text":"resultF"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:67","text":"Worley noise 纹理的结果。"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:68","text":"resultRGB"}
{"item_id":"17c9c3ef8f:69","text":"以单色颜色表示的纹理。"}
